		<div id="comment_body_64118477"><p>NASA and the US Air Force have been studying the pulse detonation engine for many years and just this year achieved some breakthrough designs using metallic 3D-printed parts.  Here is a video showing NASA's work from earlier this year.   <a href="https://youtu.be/RVxgyz_avQM" title="youtu.be">https://youtu.be/RVxgyz_avQM</a> [youtu.be]</p></div>
